{"tid":1731844,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"救下我哋","createTime":"2019-11-17T19:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T21:14:38.000Z","uid":143131,"like":68,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3231bc2712b73210dd45daaf9bb807ecf122fa23","tid":1731844,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:56:38.000Z","msg":"揾讀poly嘅frd，去聯絡住hall嘅人<br />\n帶一帶個信息<br />\n「我係一個極前線小隊嘅隊員，因為有強大嘅情報網絡所以7月至今都未試過被捕。依家想讀各位聚集一堂，諗辦法幫本部嘅手足，如果我哋依家唔幫，6am，佢哋會全滅。係本部入面，前線嘅手足係頂硬上，加上無乜點休息過，而且極多傷者又缺少fa，所以佢哋嘅情況係極之嚴峻。希望咁多位幫下佢哋，求下你哋。」"},{"pid":"27edafef4aa84a8dc4e45cdab850e890c73442c7","tid":1731844,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:56:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cba2f2403880d1aaea4d56ea9bd8cddf43c8b49","tid":1731844,"uid":149349,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:56:53.000Z","msg":"我宣布<br />\n聽朝邊個清rb就直接請佢食火魔法"},{"pid":"60c6c14e8ad826d21778ee491c5625e233798344","tid":1731844,"uid":124618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:57:00.000Z","msg":"推！！！聽朝唔好塞交通住！ ！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4eb17554929bf229bb4b65c6534cd150c650796","tid":1731844,"uid":330673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:57:09.000Z","msg":"幫我推上去 好時機沖poly<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5840290eb6bd73c0c91ea059c72b80f6d140d874","tid":1731844,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cba2f2403880d1aaea4d56ea9bd8cddf43c8b49","tid":1731844,"uid":149349,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:56:53.000Z","msg":"我宣布<br />\n聽朝邊個清rb就直接請佢食火魔法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:57:23.000Z","msg":"頂唔到聽朝"},{"pid":"1b791ff5ae2bf0fc246234b349af98ead23161af","tid":1731844,"uid":41818,"like":0